Review: Simple, works better than a roku

Name: Spacegrl
Review: I'm very happy with this item, works great and easy to set up, lots of good information about this item online, very fast delivery.

Name: Daniel
Review: Love Fire Stick and now have 2. Even though we have smart TV's have one of these plugged into each of them as they stream without glitches and buffering.Have all my apps on the stick so I can stream from my Amazon Prime account as well as Binge, Disney etc.Easy to use and set up and you can use just one remote to turn on and off the TV and control Volume so make it easier.We stream Normal Chanels through this stick also like 7 and 10 which makes it the only device we use with our TV's. Would highly recommend Fire TV sticks to anyone much better than the old Google Chrome stick we used to use.

Review: Installation of this item give me a new tv. Watching tv is such a pleasure. Would recommend it to anyone that doesn't own smart tv. Apps work perfectly. Very happy.
